HTML -- Hyper Test Markup Language.

HTML TAGS- <html>,<head>, <title>, <body>, 

html- html is the starting of any html coding .
head- in head we can define any headings .
title - title is the name of your open tab .
body - we can create our whole page in body .

<br> - to add a break in a line ..

<p align=center> text </p> -> align can be - left, right, center, justified. 

HTML TEXT STYLES -- <b>, <i>, <s>,<u>, <tt>  -- bold, italic, strikethrough, underline, testwriter text

HTML LISTS-- list are 3 types
1-
<ul type="circle"> unordered list 
<li> -> to take option in circle or square..
<li> Basic  <li> C <li> Java <li> Fortran <li> JavaScript
</ul>
2-
<ol> -> ORDER LIST LIKE - 1,2,3,4, (OPTIONS)
</ol>

3- 
<dl> Defination list..
<dt> defination topic.. Like-- ( Keyboard)
<dd> complete defination ..
note- <dt> <dd> close ni honge..
</dl>

<blockquote>  I am trying to apply blockquote here .  block quote means line will start 
              after some spacing ..
</blockquote>

-> How we can Write cemical reactions & arithmetic formulas .. here we learn about that..
use <sup> digit </sup> for upper digit like - a2+b2
use <sub> digit </sub> for lower digit like - h2o


-->> To Link Pages ( four types of linking we can do in html  ) 
1-Linking to other web Pages..

<a href= "Cardekho.html"> Visit CarDekho</a> <br>
<a href= "Bikedekho.html"> Visit BikeDekho</a> 

2-Links within a page..
3-Links to a specific part of another page ..
4- E-mail links..

HTML Document Tables-->>
to make tables you have to start with <table> .... </table> tag. with table tag we will  use <tr>..<tr>, <td>..</td> and <th>..</th> tags

1-> in <table> we can use -- Border, cellspacing, cellpadding-the amount of space between the edges of the cell and its contents.,width, bgcolor,background,..
2-> <tr>..</tr> defines a table row -- align, valign,bgcolor, background,. (TR- TABLE ROW)
3-> <th> .. </th> defines a table heading cell its attributes are -- align, valign, rowspan, colspan, width , bgcolor, background (TH-TABLE HEADING) [rowspan & colspan means merging between cells ]
4-> <td> ..</td> defines a table data cell .. -- align, valign, rowspan,colspan,width bgcolor, background. (TD- TABLE DATA)

if we want to add any image in cells then [ <tr> <td><img src="filename.html"> 
 note-->> <tr>,<th>,<td> close ni honge only <table> close hogi ..

HTML IMAGES -- >>

 to add image with the help of this tag -->> <img src="picture.png">
[ align - left, right, bottom, top , height, width, border, hspace - horizontal space , vspace - vertical space ..

HTML MULTIMEDIA -->>

  to add sound & video in a web page with the help of <audio controls>
  <source src="sakhiya.mp3" type="audio/ogg" >
</audio>

to add video in a web page with the help of 
<video width="400" controls>
  <source src="mov_bbb.mp4" type="video/mp4">
</video>



HTML FORMS -->>
the HTML <form> element defines a form that is used to collect user input .. 
<form>  .... form elements ..... </form>

the <input> element

   input types are many types it can be text, radio, submit , password , reset , check box , button & so on ...
<input type="text" or "radio" or "submit" or "password" or "reset" or "color" or "date" or "datetime-local" or "email" or "file" "month" (month is not supported in safari , firefox, internetExplorer earlier than 11 version.. ) or "number" min="1" max"10" or "range" min="1" max="10" or "time" or "search"or.......>

-->> use <form action="/action_page.php"> for submit form & get it to other page ..

